ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"原來今日12.23有「灣仔:和你坐。stuck稅局」？<br />\n又係冇人去？"},{"pid":"05c6b6eef34c62cff2e3e92d9cd14d6b5e301500","tid":1794910,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"運動的確有降溫跡象<br />\n但好大原因係文宣不足同埋活動目標唔夠清晰<br />\n大家可以睇睇其實呢幾個星期突然多咗好多集會同活動<br />\n就係因為有堆散水撚喺民陣遊行之後吹失敗風<br />\n跟住有好多搞手都驚真係散結果係咁搞活動<br />\n最後不斷消耗行動力<br />\n結果連連登行動post都推唔起<br />\n係呢一兩日先好番好多<br />\n<br />\n希望遊行集會行動搞手可以更well plan<br />\n講明每一次活動目標<br />\n其實有樣嘢冇錯<br />\n係唔少和理非都要講埋出聲先知要做咩<br />\n所以有活動嘅時候<br />\n除咗叫和理非出嚟<br />\n仲要清晰俾佢地知道自己做緊咩<br />\n<br />\n同埋地區活動可以加埋入地區連儂牆度宣傳<br />\n當然大行動優先宣傳<br />\n暫時嚟講較可行係走番地區性活動"},{"pid":"147dbcd502bdd16eb940129f36d69e6ba77643f6","tid":1794910,"uid":262248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"文宣少左好多"},{"pid":"12845787d1fb708d744792a9141f2f1858891e53","tid":1794910,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:59:44.000Z","msg":"10點鳩叫，9月開學就冇影<br />\n<br />\n曾經係威係勢既春袋機場，一張又臨時又無限期既禁制令，加幾個食蕉就收晒皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8076011f637493bbdd027425c287fb9b78bc4e","tid":1794910,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:51:02.000Z","msg":"所羅門發起白宮聯署要人！<br />\n<br />\n取消北京2022冬季奧運，簽極唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/ask-international-olympics-commission-corporate-sponsors-relocate-or-cancel-beijing-2022-winter-olympics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fask-international-olympics-commission-corporate-sponsors-relocate-or-cancel-beijing-2022-winter-olympics&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwZq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=5bb9a4a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petit